</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Devil's Island</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span id="coordinates"><a href="/wiki/Geographic_coordinate_system" title="Geographic coordinate system">Coordinates</a>: <span class="plainlinks nourlexpansion"><a class="external text" href="//tools.wmflabs.org/geohack/geohack.php?pagename=Devil%27s_Island&amp;params=5.293611_N_52.583056_W_"><span class="geo-nondefault"><span class="geo-dms" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location"><span class="latitude">5°17′37″N</span> <span class="longitude">52°34′59″W</span></span></span><span class="geo-multi-punct">﻿ / ﻿</span><span class="geo-default"><span class="geo-dec" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location">5.293611°N 52.583056°W</span><span style="display:none">﻿ / <span class="geo">5.293611; -52.583056</span></span></span></a></span></span></span></p>
<div class="hatnote">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Devils_Island_(disambiguation)" title="Devils Island (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Devils Island</a>.</div>
